description: The diff-match-patch-es library has a different API from the old diff-match-patch library
impact-type: compatibility-break

Plugins that use the `diff-match-patch` library directly will need to update their code:

* The default export and class constructor have been removed; use the named function exports instead
* Function names are now camelCase (e.g. `diffMain` instead of `diff_main`)
* Options such as `Diff_Timeout` and `Diff_EditCost` are now passed as an options object argument rather than being set as properties
